column1: Daily Weather Observations for Nowra, New South Wales for August 2021
Prepared at 16:00 UTC on Saturday 16 October 2021   IDCJDW2101.202108
Some cloud observations are from automated equipment; these are somewhat different to those made by a human observer and may not appear every day.
Observations were drawn from Nowra RAN Air Station AWS {station 068072}
